CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "Historian" (
	"ID"	INTEGER NOT NULL,
	"fecha_hora" TEXT NOT NULL,
	"robot"	INTEGER NOT NULL,
	"eje"	INTEGER NOT NULL,
	"corriente"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"temperatura"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"pos_actual"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"pos_meta"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"torque"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"torque_factor"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"error"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"carga_x"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"carga_y"	REAL NOT NULL,
	"carga_z"	REAL NOT NULL,
	PRIMARY KEY("ID" AUTOINCREMENT)
);

<script id="titleScript" type="text/javascript">

     //add logo
       $('#logooptimotion').remove();
       $('#logofg').remove();
       $('#clock').remove();
        $('.extra').remove();
        
        var div1 = $('<div class="extra"/>');
        var logo = new Image();

        logo.src = 'data:image/png;base64,'
        logo.width = 200;
        logo.height = 45;
        logo.id = 'logooptimotion';
        div1[0].style.margin = 'auto 10px auto auto';
        
       // var div2 = $('<div class="extra"/>');
        var logo1 = new Image();
        
        logo1.src = 'data:image/jpeg;base64,';
        logo1.width = 150;
        logo1.height = 45;
        logo1.id = 'logofg';
        //div2[0].style.margin = 'auto 10px auto auto';
        

       // div1.append(logo);
       // div1.append('  ');
       // div1.append(logo1);

        function addToToolbar() {
            var toolbar = $('.md-toolbar-tools');
            
            if(!toolbar.length) return;
            
            toolbar.append(div1);
        }
        addToToolbar();
    $('#clock').remove();
    var toolbar = $('.md-toolbar-tools');
    var div = $('<div class="extra clock"/>');
    var p = $('<p/ id="clock">');
    
    $('#titleScript').parent().hide();
    div.append(p);
    div[0].style.margin = '5px 5px 5px auto';
    toolbar.append(div);

    function displayTitle(lh) {
        p.text(lh); 
    }
    
    function upTime() {
        var d = new Date();
        p.text(d.toLocaleTimeString('de-AT'));
    }

    

    // Watch the payload and update the title
    (function(scope) {
        scope.$watch('msg.payload', function(data) {
            displayTitle(data);
        });
        setInterval(upTime,1000);
    })(scope);
</script>
